data.name: Privacy policies
data.value:
Protecting your privacy is important and fundamental to us. We hope the following statement helps you understand how our application handles personally identifiable information ('PII').

In general, we do not collect your PII when you download our application. To be specific, we do not require consumers to register before downloading the application, nor do we track consumer visits to our application, we do not even have a server to store such PII.

Information that We collect

Cookies - The application saves settings that the end user wants to make in the application, for example, dark mode and language. At no time will we ask for your personal information to enter or request any application service

How do we use and information?

With the above, your personal information is secure and does not have no risk of your data being exposed. At the moment, we will not ask for personal data, but in the future it may be required to save data in a database in the cloud and have an online service. In general, you can be attentive in all our official contacts of any change in the service.
